    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Privacy policy</h2>
    <p>This privacy policy explains why the Ministry of Justice collects personal data when you use the Ask a question service.</p>
    <p>The policy also explains:</p>

    <%= govuk_list [
        "how we store this data",
